# SmartLocalServiceBooking 🛠️

A lightweight, Flask-powered web application designed to connect local service providers with customers. Features full role-based access control (RBAC) for Users, Service Providers, and Admins.

---

## 🚀 Features

- **Authentication & Authorization:** Secure user registration, login, and role-based views.
- **Customer Portal:** Browse available local services, view details, and place bookings.
- **Provider Dashboard:** Create service listings, manage availability, and handle incoming booking requests.
- **Admin Management:** Comprehensive overview to monitor users, services, and overall booking metrics.
- **Quick Setup:** Pre-configured database initialization script with pre-seeded test data.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* **Backend:** Python 3.x, Flask
* **Database:** SQLite
* **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (Jinja2 Templates)

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```text
SmartLocalServiceBooking/
├── templates/          # Jinja2 HTML templates
├── static/             # CSS stylesheets, JavaScript, and images
├── app.py              # Main Flask application logic & routing
├── init_db.py          # Database setup and sample seed data generator
├── database.db         # SQLite database (generated after init)
├── requirements.txt    # Python package dependencies
├── run.bat             # Helper script (Windows Command Prompt)
└── run.ps1             # Helper script (Windows PowerShell)
